import React from 'react';

import {
  ProgramName,
  FieldHeader,
  FieldValue,
  Container,
  CollegeName,
  Logo,
} from './ProgramRow.styles';

import a from '../../.next/static/images/santarosajuniorcollege.svg'

const ProgramRow = () => (
  <Container>
    <Logo src={'https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/2x/googlelogo_color_160x56dp.png'}></Logo>
    <ProgramName>Information Technology</ProgramName>
    <CollegeName>Santa Rosa Junior College</CollegeName>
    <FieldHeader start={4} end={5}>
      Degree Type
    </FieldHeader>
    <FieldValue start={4} end={5}>
      Associate's
    </FieldValue>
    <FieldHeader start={5} end={6}>
      Delivery
    </FieldHeader>
    <FieldValue start={5} end={6}>
      100% Fully Online
    </FieldValue>
    <FieldHeader start={6} end={7}>
      Annual Tuition
    </FieldHeader>
    <FieldValue start={6} end={7}>
      $1,375
    </FieldValue>
  </Container>
);

export default ProgramRow;
